  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/50px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/75px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/100px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Ketter</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/50px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/75px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/100px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Ketter</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Ranger\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ranger\">ranger</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a>. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ketter&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ketter&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ketter is part of the escort for Lord Commander <a href=\"/index.php/Jeor_Mormont\" title=\"Jeor Mormont\">Jeor Mormont</a> when he goes to inspect the corpses of <a href=\"/index.php/Othor\" title=\"Othor\">Othor</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jafer_Flowers\" title=\"Jafer Flowers\">Jafer Flowers</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Haunted_forest\" title=\"Haunted forest\">haunted forest</a>. When they attempt to load the corpses on the horses, one almost bites Ketter.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ketter&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite